{"tid":2418140,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"(股價如入無人之境！)駕 Tesla 無人墓園行走   螢幕顯示有行人極恐怖","createTime":"2021-02-22T11:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T16:00:25.000Z","uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a053d415febae94f8a467c22e61bc17e215d54b","tid":2418140,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"駕 Tesla 無人墓園行走   螢幕顯示有行人極恐怖<br />\n<br />\n虎仔 / 馬日山(uniqlo) 2021-02-22 09:38<br />\n<br />\n要數一部滿載高科技的電動車，相信很多人都會馬上想到 Tesla，他們的電動車安裝了大量鏡頭和感應器，汽車系統能夠通過這些感應器偵測車輛附近的物件，無論是汽車或行人，都會在汽車的中控台螢幕顯示出來。最近有 Tesla 車主就分享了他們的恐怖又靈異個人經歷。<br />\n <br />\n駕 Tesla 無人墓園行走   螢幕顯示有行人極恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前有外國車主表示自己駕駛 Tesla 在空無一人的墓地行駛，中控台螢幕不斷顯示附近有人正在走動...<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">網址有片</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/27778/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1141%2F27778%2F1%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=88d8245a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/27778/1/</a>"},{"pid":"d7b8a4fdbd52a7d8708842cc61392ef2e40479cf","tid":2418140,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"冇人有相同經歷咩？"},{"pid":"2cb907cb8ead9f3f0e08993f0abc180725599186","tid":2418140,"uid":118988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:56:38.000Z","msg":"Scan到墓碑當人啫，光天化日驚西咩"},{"pid":"99c915c8cd2a262c647a83890c197bdbc8f6f3f5","tid":2418140,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEkd66j.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEkd66j.gif&h=4d3ca39f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb3e298b8211547c20a1536d83074e43eaf93086","tid":2418140,"uid":319138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<br />\n有安心上路<img src=